imdb.plot outline: A Pocketful of Dublin is an online interactive documentary which aims to capture a sense of the area and community around Saint Patrick's Cathedral and the Iveagh Trust's Bull Alley Estate. This tiny geographical location has a rich and diverse history. Through the words of the current tenants, regular visitors, businesses, previous residents and even the pets, we delve into various aspects of the community past and present.
imdb.title: Pocketful of Dublin
